<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>
    <b>Rent a Car</b> is committed to protecting the privacy of our customers. 
    This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use
    our rent-a-car services, including our website and mobile application. Please read this Privacy
    Policy carefully. By accessing or using our services, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.
</p>

<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>

<p>
    We may collect personal information from you when you use our services, make a reservation, 
    contact us, or otherwise interact with our website or mobile application. This information may include:
</p>

<ul>
   <li>Your Name</li>
   <li>Contact information (email address)</li>
</ul>

<h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>

<p>We may use the information we collect from you to:</p>

<ul>
    <li>Process reservations</li>
    <li>Provide customer support</li>
    <li>Communicate with you about your reservations and our services</li>
    <li>Personalize your experience</li>
    <li>Improve our services and develop new features</li>
    <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. Information Sharing</h2>

<p>We may share your information with third parties, including:</p>

<ul>
    <li>Service providers who assist us in operating our business (e.g., payment processors, vehicle suppliers)</li>
    <li>Legal authorities or law enforcement agencies if required by law or to protect our rights or the safety of others</li>
    <li>Business partners or affiliates for marketing or promotional purposes (with your consent)</li>
</ul>

<h2>4. Data Security</h2>

<p>
    We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, use, 
    or disclosure. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage
    is 100% secure. Therefore, we cannot guarantee absolute security.
</p>
<h2>5. Your Choices</h2>

<p>
    You may choose not to provide certain information, but this may limit your ability to use some of our services.
    You can update or delete your information by contacting us.
</p>

<h2>6. Updates to this Privacy Policy</h2>

<p>
    We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, 
    and the "last updated" date will be revised accordingly. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy 
    periodically for any updates.</p>

